---
title: Carb Smart Chorizo Taco Salad Bowls with Pico de Gallo and Creamy Lemon Dressing
description: Bulk up your bowl with this taco salad! Fresh DIY pico de gallo, cheddar cheese, guacamole and a creamy lime dressing will fill you up, but without the starch.

